#MEM id=ui source=/root/yvon/agent-department/Technical/mia/skills/ui/02-tailwind.md
M|ui|priority: high
M|ui|applies-to: ui
M|ui|load: always
M|ui|model: qwen3.5-4b
M|ui|conflicts: []
M|ui|Follow Prettier Tailwind plugin order:
M|ui|1. Layout (display, position, z-index)
M|ui|2. Box model (w, h, m, p)
M|ui|3. Typography (font, text, leading)
M|ui|4. Visual (bg, border, shadow, opacity)
M|ui|5. Interactive (hover, focus, active)
M|ui|6. Responsive (sm:, md:, lg:)
M|ui|- Use semantic class extraction for repeated patterns: `@apply` in globals.css
M|ui|- Never use arbitrary values `[17px]` when a standard token works
M|ui|- Dark mode: always use `dark:` prefix, never manual class switching
M|ui|- Never use `\!important` — fix specificity properly
M|ui|- Never use inline styles — always Tailwind or CSS modules
M|ui|- Don't mix Tailwind with styled-components or emotion
M|ui|```tsx
M|ui|// ✅ Good — readable, ordered
M|ui|<div className="flex items-center gap-4 px-6 py-4 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
M|ui|// ❌ Bad — arbitrary values, no order
M|ui|<div className="hover:shadow-md flex shadow-sm px-6 bg-white gap-4 py-4 rounded-xl items-center">
M|ui|```